t_ar": "مَفْسَدَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S and Msb and K in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fsd", "text_ar": "فسد"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ";)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a good, right,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "virtuous, affair;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(KL;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a thing that is good and right;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn. ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SalaAHN", "text_ar": "صَلَاحٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[q. v.]: pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maSaAliHu", "text_ar": "مَصَالِحُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, A, Msb, K.) One says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "naZara fiY maSAliHi Aln~aAsi", "text_ar": "نَظَرَ فِى مَصالِحِ النَّاسِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He considered the things that were for the good of the people"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "humo mino A^aholi", "text_ar": "هُمْ مِنْ اَهْلِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlmafaAsidi laA AlmaSaAliHi", "text_ar": "المَفَاسِدِ لَا المَصَالِحِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They are of the people who occupy themselves in the things conducive to evil, not the things conducive to good"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A, TA. *) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiY AlA^amori maSolaHapN", "text_ar": "فِى الاَمْرِ مَصْلَحَةٌ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "In the affair is that which is good:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb:) [or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a cause of good."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "raA^aY AlA_imaAmu AlmaSolaHapa fiY ka*aA", "text_ar": "رَاَى الاـِمَامُ المَصْلَحَةَ فِى كَذَا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The Imám saw what was good and right"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what was conducive to good"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in such a thing."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b2-  It is also an inf. n. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SalaHa", "text_ar": "صَلَحَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (MA.)"}], "source_refs": ["Msb"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}